{{champion:154}} 
Zac is fun, definitely not the best in lane. You usually just want to farm up for late game and be a tanky CC machine. The passive is great bait though. I've had so many people tower dive me just to see me pop out into a few blobs and then the turret finishes them off. I usually build something like:
{{item:3260}} {{item:3065}} {{item:3143}} {{item:3116}} {{item:3083}} {{item:3151}} 
Like any good build it varies depending on the situation but you basically want to be super tanky and have just a little bit of damage tacked on so you can be a potential threat by yourself.

Use {{champion:133}}, She is the best lane bully you can get, as far as builds go i get
{{item:3087}} {{item:3072}} {{item:3252}} {{item:3031}}  {{item:3142}} {{item:3078}} 
and take {{summoner:4}} {{summoner:14}}  or{{summoner:12}} {{summoner:6}}
